cat << EOF
This package provides functionality for generalising the deriving mechanism
in Haskell to arbitrary classes. It was first described in the paper:

A generic deriving mechanism for Haskell. Jose Pedro Magalhaes, Atze Dijkstra,
Johan Jeuring, and Andres Loeh. Haskell'10.

The current implementation integrates with the new GHC Generics.
EOF
